Paper: hep-th/9904159

Date: 1999-04-23

Title: Pauli's Term and Fractional Spin

Authors: F. A. S. Nobre and C. A. S. Almeida (Departamento de

Fisica-UFC-Brazil)Comments: 7 pages, no figures. To appear in Physics Letters B

Journal-ref: Phys.Lett. B455 (1999) 213-216

In this work we consider an Abelian Chern-Simons-Higgs model couplednon-minimally to matter fields. This coupling is implemented by means of aPauli-type coupling. We show that the Pauli term is sufficient to gives rise tofractional spin.